content: That's really helpful, thanks! I think I'll start with my living room and sort through all the stuff I've accumulated over the years. I'm sure I'll find some old photos from my trip to the beach with Rachel and Mike that I need to sort through and share with them. By the way, do you have any tips on how to organize my digital life, like my phone and computer? I feel like I have a ton of files and photos scattered all over the place.
